# GitHub Branch Sync Skill Equivalent

- Use `./scripts/sync-personality-branches.ps1` when `main` and `persona/*` branches need one batch push or pull against GitHub.
- Start with `-DryRun` when you want to inspect the sync plan first.
- Use `-Mode push` to publish local personality branches.
- Use `-Mode pull` to fetch and fast-forward local branches from GitHub.
- Treat pull failures as branch-state problems to resolve explicitly; do not replace `ff-only` sync with implicit merges.